This dataset was obtained from the OpenNeuro project (https://www.openneuro.org). Accession #: ds004495

Description: Episodic and Semantic Memory fMRI Dataset

Authors:
Roni Tibon
Andrea Greve
Gina Humphreys
Alexander J. Quent
Rik Henson

Please cite the following reference if you use these data:

     XXX

Additional information related to the project, including accepted version of Stage 1 protocol, is available on https://osf.io/dm47y/ 

==================================================================================

func/
-----
Two session for each participants: 
	ses-EP:  Episodic task
	ses-SEM: Semantic task + Control task 

For each task: 
	Multiple runs (3 for EP and 2 for SEM/VIS)
	4 echos  


anat/
-----
Anatomical preprocessed data are located under /derivatives. These are defaced and normalised T1 images (for GDPR compliance).   


behavdata/
----------
Behavioural data from the study phase (EP+SEM), test phase (all tasks), and debriefing phase (EP) 

 
